snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - Akuma Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Messatsu! The legendary Akuma will consume all hope, fear, and nothingness when he comes to Street Fighter 6 this spring. Find him in the new World Tour area, Gokuento, where you may ask him to be your Master...if you dare.

Owners of the Deluxe and Ultimate Edition or the Year 1 Character Pass and Ultimate Pass of Street Fighter 6 will obtain Akuma when he releases.

https://streetfighter.com/6/

#StreetFighter6 #Capcom #Akuma
